= SDL_GetNumVideoDrivers =
Use this function to get the number of video drivers compiled into SDL.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_GetNumVideoDrivers(void)
```

== Return Value ==
Returns an integer >=1 on success or a negative error code on failure; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

